  34. let ksprintf k (Format (fmt, _)) =
  35.   let k' acc =
  36.     let buf = Buffer.create 64 in
  37.     strput_acc buf acc;
  38.     k (Buffer.contents buf) in
  39.   make_printf k' End_of_acc fmt
